===Noun===
# The act or sound of tolling

===Verb===
'''to toll''' ([[tolls]], [[tolled]], [[tolling]])
# To make the noise of a [[bell]]
#:''For whom the bell tolls.''
# To ring a bell slowly and repeatedly
# To announce by tolling
#:''the bells tolled the King’s death''

